ITV Tour De France 2012 Stage 8 Highlights PDTV x264 AAC

Presented by Gary Imlach, Chris Boardman and Ned Boulting. Commentary: Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen. Stage 8, Belfort to Porrentruy. At only 154 km, a short stage for the Tour riders although seven categorised climbs make today's stage a trial for the non-climbers. A long-range attack could make it home today and complicate the fight for the general classification.
